data.title: Jared's Counting Crows Discography
data.text:
Title: Across A Wire: Live in New York

Catalog Number: DGCD2-25222

Record Label(s): DavidGeffenCompany

Format: 2CD Digipak

Released: 1997

Track List:..............................................

Disc 1 (Recorded at Chelsea Studios in New York on August 12, 1997 for "VH1 Storytellers"):

Round Here - 6:16

Have You Seen Me Lately? - 3:57

Angels Of The Silences - 3:57

Catapult - 3:57

Mr. Jones - 5:17

Rain King - 5:51

Mercury - 3:45

Ghost Train - 5:27

Anna Begins - 6:35

Chelsea - 6:15

Disc 2 (Recorded at Hammerstein Ballroom in New York on November 6, 1997 for "MTV Live From The 10 Spot"):

Recovering The Satellites - 5:49

Angels Of The Silences - 3:34

Rain King - 5:48

Sullivan Street - 4:37

Children In Bloom - 5:19

Have You Seen Me Lately? - 4:10

Raining In Baltimore - 5:34

Round Here - 10:00

I'm Not Sleeping - 4:58

A Murder Of One - 5:35

A Long December - 6:06

Walkaways -1:50

Notes:

Chelsea is a previously unreleased track and is not part of the VH1 setlist.

"VH1 Storytellers" was released as a promotional CD by Geffen Records prior to the release of this CD.

The VH1 set does not contain A Long December, which appeared on the original broadcast, or Omaha, Good Luck, and Walkaways, which were played but not broadcast.

Round Here, Mercury, and Anna Begins were not aired on VH1.

The MTV set does not contain Goodnight Elizabeth, Catapult, Mr. Jones, Omaha, and Anna Begins, which appeared on the original broadcast, or Wiseblood and Daylight Fading, which were played but not broadcast.

Raining In Baltimore and Children In Bloom were not aired on MTV.

Title: Live At The Fox Theatre

Catalog Number: INT5P-6728

Record Label(s): Geffen

Format: CD (sleeve)

Released: November 2, 1999

Track List:..............................................

Mercury (Live in Colorado on August 17, 1999) - 8:18

Omaha (Live in Colorado on August 17, 1999) - 4:14

Another Horsedreamers Blues (Live in Colorado on August 17, 1999) - 5:22

Goodnight Elisabeth (Live in Colorado on August 17, 1999) - 6:44

Notes:

All tracks were recorded at the Fox Theatre in Boulder.

This is a limited edition promotional EP given away at Best Buy stores with the purchase of "This Desert Life" on the day of its' release.
